[Title]  Bastard Bass Mix
[Artist] Ghislain Poirier
[Album]  No Ground Under Promo
[Format] MP3
[KB/S]   192

Ghislain Poirier is set to release his Ninja Tune debut No Ground Under in the U.S. this month, and the bass-obsessed Montreal DJ/producer has assembled a 40-minute megamix that sets his album&amp;#039;s grime-, ragga-, dancehall-, Baltimore club-, and crunk-infused beats alongside his remixes of tracks by Dizzee Rascal, Lil Wayne, and others. There&amp;#039;s a lot here to get heads nodding, including two versions of Poirier&amp;#039;s &quot;Blazin&quot; that aren&amp;#039;t built to sell Toyotas.

